    "description": "《Swordship》是一款未来主义的快节奏躲避游戏，它颠覆了传统街机射击游戏的剧本。在敌人一心想把你的飞剑快艇撕成碎片的强大压力下，通过躲避、穿梭和潜入的方式，扭转战局并战胜敌人。<br><br>这款令人上瘾的动作roguelike冒险游戏需要你在瞬间做出决定，为你带来反对暴政和不公正的光荣胜利，成为被放逐伙伴的希望象征，或是成为无名英雄沉入海底。伴随着即将成为现代经典的配乐，这款游戏将带你进入一个阴郁的未来水世界。<br> <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804270/extras/d42f7852e6a8c6cce2748a1a21a885e1.poster.avif?t=1759330818\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804270/extras/d42f7852e6a8c6cce2748a1a21a885e1.webm?t=1759330818\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804270/extras/d42f7852e6a8c6cce2748a1a21a885e1.mp4?t=1759330818\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804270/extras/c20c61730d1dfc4703a1d3a5adbc3bab.avif?t=1759330818\" width=601 height=180 /></span><br><br>枪炮很酷，但躲避是你最好的武器：飞剑快艇的机动性可以让你通过战术走位和躲避敌人的炮火来智取敌人。<br> <br>快艇能力：收集提高动力的组件，在航行过程中尝试不同的玩法<br> <br><br>风险/奖励升级：是选择冒险将被盗的货柜存入银行提高分数，还是选择安全的被动升级和额外的快艇，这取决于你自己的游戏方格<br> <br><br>天气：学习掌握不同的天气状况，以通过随机生成的关卡。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804270/extras/28abbbe463f88aac60600c05abcae6f4.poster.avif?t=1759330818\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804270/extras/28abbbe463f88aac60600c05abcae6f4.webm?t=1759330818\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804270/extras/28abbbe463f88aac60600c05abcae6f4.mp4?t=1759330818\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804270/extras/3dcbc3d5167028ac12454eb2781b7bdb.avif?t=1759330818\" width=601 height=180 /></span><br><br>游戏背景设在全球变暖后的世界。人类逃到海底生存，生活于三座规模庞大的海底城市。<br> <br>少数人因居住空间不足而被驱逐出城市，只好在炙热的大地上设法活下去。与此同时，这些巨型城市每天会运输上百万个货柜，里面装满所需物资。<br><br>几个海底城市的居民擅于操控速度飞快的船只，于是他们开始拦截这些价值连城的货柜，将物资运送给被放逐的伙伴。<br><br>拦截货柜的成功率因人而异。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804270/extras/c7e7d5f0fa1bae856df65bfeece7d895.poster.avif?t=1759330818\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804270/extras/c7e7d5f0fa1bae856df65bfeece7d895.webm?t=1759330818\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804270/extras/c7e7d5f0fa1bae856df65bfeece7d895.mp4?t=1759330818\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
